import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  import { Playground } from 'docz';

export default ({components, ...props}) => <MDXTag name="wrapper"  components={components}>
<MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"test"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h1" props={{"aria-hidden":true,"href":"#test"}}><MDXTag name="span" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"className":"icon-link"}}>{`#`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>{`Test`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`Test code`}</MDXTag>
